description:
Divide trail, formerly Hiway 1a, is now a bike and cross country ski trail 
long the former road.
Pleasant ride with some great scenery in places. Crosses into BC and 
ends at the start of the road to Lake O'Hara.
directions:
Road to Lake Louise from the village just below Deer Lodge, parking lot 
on 
right (heading towards Lake Louise)
title: Divide Trail (formerly Hwy 1A)
